        <div class="hero-text">
            <h3 class="title"><a href="/news/the-newest-story-from-mark-twain-the-purloining-of-prince-oleomargarine/">The newest story from Mark Twain</a></h3>
                          <p class="dek"><a href="/news/the-newest-story-from-mark-twain-the-purloining-of-prince-oleomargarine/">
Literary scholars and husband-and-wife children's book illustrators turn fragments of a long-lost Samuel Clemens story into a book, "The Purloining of Prince Oleomargarine"</a></p>
                    </div>
        <a href="/news/the-newest-story-from-mark-twain-the-purloining-of-prince-oleomargarine/" class="">
